title: Dare to DJ with Tigerlily
itunes:title: Dare to DJ with Tigerlily
description:
LIVE from the 2022 JBL Fest in Las Vegas, Betty Who is joined by Tigerlily IRL! A fellow Australian and musician, Tigerlily reveals how she took a shot on herself to become a celebrated and highly acclaimed DJ in the global music scene. In our season finale, Betty Who asks Tigerlily about how she cultivated confidence as an artist and found balance and boundaries that help her continually show up for her fans and for herself. Tigerlily also emphasizes the importance of using her platform for more than just positive vibes. There is no better way to close the first season of “Unfiltered: The JBL Podcast,” than to hear the energy and inspiration shared live at JBL Fest this year! 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
